ttp_template:
<group name="cryptomap_encryption_hash_interface">
  Crypto Map: {{CRYPTOMAP | ORPHRASE}}
  Local  Addr: {{SABUNDLE | ORPHRASE}}92.168.0.1
  Security Protocol: {{PROTOCOL | ORPHRASE}}
Interface: {{INTERFACE | ORPHRASE}}
  Local  Addr: {{LOCAL_ADDR | ORPHRASE}}
  Remote Addr: {{REMOTE_ADDR | ORPHRASE}}
  Encryption: {{ENCRYPTION}}, Hash: {{HASH | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
cli_content:
Interface: Tunnel0
    Crypto Map: CMAP
    Local  Addr: 192.168.0.1
    Remote Addr: 192.168.0.2
    SABundle: 2 active IPsec SAs
    Security Protocol: ESP
    Encryption: AES-256, Hash: SHA-256

Interface: Tunnel1
    Crypto Map: CMAP
    Local  Addr: 10.1.1.1
    Remote Addr: 10.1.1.2
    SABundle: 1 active IPsec SA
    Security Protocol: ESP
    Encryption: AES-128, Hash: SHA-1
textfsm_template:
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value CRYPTOMAP (\S+)
Value LOCAL_ADDR (\S+)
Value REMOTE_ADDR (\S+)
Value SABUNDLE (\d+)
Value PROTOCOL (\S+)
Value ENCRYPTION ([\S\s]+)
Value HASH (\S+)

Start
  ^Interface:\s+${INTERFACE}\s*$$
  ^\s+Crypto\s+Map:\s+${CRYPTOMAP}\s*$$
  ^\s+Local\s+Addr:\s+${LOCAL_ADDR}\s*$$
  ^\s+Remote\s+Addr:\s+${REMOTE_ADDR}\s*$$
  ^\s+SABundle:\s+${SABUNDLE}\s+active\s+IPsec\s+SAs*\s*$$
  ^\s+Security\s+Protocol:\s+${PROTOCOL}\s*$$
  ^\s+Encryption:\s+${ENCRYPTION},\s+Hash:\s+${HASH}\s*$$ -> Record
